cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with machine learning and specifically focuses on federated learning and domain adaptation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with image and text classification tasks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of adversarial techniques and attention mechanisms suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of feature disentanglement suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
